  <brief_title>Neutrophil Gelatinase-associated Lipocalin as a New Biomarker to Detect Acute Kidney Injury in Postoperative Cardiac Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>NGAL as a Marker of Acute Kidney Injury After Cardiac Surgery. Observational Study</official_title>
  <sponsors>
